    "300706": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Dunyarzad",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Badis",
                    "T": "...Tch, we're too late. Who knew the little lady was such an early riser."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idder",
                    "T": "I know, right... Hey, wait a minute. Boss, isn't that her?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Badis",
                    "T": "Oh, that most certainly is! We're in luck. She's walking right into our clutches."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Those Eremites don't look like they're up to any good..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "...Who are you? I don't believe the Homayanis hired you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Badis",
                    "T": "Heh, that's right. We haven't received any of their Mora, but... I wonder how much the Homayanis would shell out to get you back?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "They're a gang of kidnappers! Traveler, hurry and protect Dunyarzad!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We'll be fine..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Professional here, ready to go."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Hey! Did you scumbags even consider that the Homayanis might've hired a merc that outclasses you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Badis",
                    "T": "You're... Dehya!? Dehya the Flame-Mane... No wonder we mercs haven't heard anything about you for so long. You sold your unruly mane to the highest bidder."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "Don't speak so disrespectfully. My family started working with her as gratitude for her past kindness to us..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Don't worry about it, my lady. Just some friendly banter between mercs. One punch and those rabid dogs will expose themselves for what they really are."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Badis",
                    "T": "Hmph, aren't your claws all dull by now? Don't get too cocky!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Traveler, take Miss Dunyarzad to a safe location."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "No, we're gonna stay and help. There's too many of them!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We can't guarantee anyone's safety here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Dehya's top priority is her employer's safety."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hm... You're right. Alright, fine!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "Please be careful, Dehya."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Don't waste your time worrying about me — this is my job. Look out for yourself. After I've wiped the floor with them, I'll go find you all."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
