    "300804": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Dunyarzad",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Phaki",
                    "T": "Farris! Farris!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vihar",
                    "T": "Alright soldiers, now that you have your Yalda Candies, don't forget your loyalty to Lesser Lord Kusanali. Dismissed!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Phaki",
                    "T": "Yes, Knight Farris!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's going on? Is this a play?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "Farris, the Knight of Flowers, is another Sabzeruz Festival icon, and one immensely popular with children."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vihar",
                    "T": "Haha, it's all thanks to Miss Dunyarzad's sponsorship that the children can meet the Knight of Flowers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vihar",
                    "T": "Oh, do you want some Yalda Candies? I happen to have some boxes readied here. Take a look and pick whichever one you want."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uhh, what's to pick? Don't these boxes all look the same?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vihar",
                    "T": "Haha, it's not that simple. Each box contains a random flavor — it's up to the luck of the draw. Flavors include Lavender Melon, Harra Fruit, Sunsettia..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ooh, how interesting!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vihar",
                    "T": "...And there's also Lizard Tail and Onikabuto."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ugh! Why do those flavors even exist!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... Traveler, help Paimon pick one. Paimon wants to eat the Sunsettia flavor!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vihar",
                    "T": "Great. These boxes of candy are numbered one to five from left to right. Which one do you want?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Number one."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's definitely number one."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Number two."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's definitely number two."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Number three."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's definitely number three."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Number four."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's definitely number four."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vihar",
                    "T": "Ah, excellently chosen! Number four is indeed Sunsettia."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Haha, Paimon bet you had incredible luck, and Paimon was right!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That just now... I don't think that was luck."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I don't know why, but I knew it must have been number four."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? How's that possible? It's obviously random..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Number five."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's definitely number five."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let me give it a little thought..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Vihar",
                    "T": "Ah, excellently chosen! Number four is indeed Sunsettia."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Haha, Paimon bet you had incredible luck, and Paimon was right!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Just now... Did I really mean to choose number four?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It felt like... my body just subconsciously reached for it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? Are you saying that you instinctively chose the right box?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm, but now that you mention it... Paimon also had the feeling you'd choose the right one... Is that kinda like what you felt?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Why do I keep having this sense of déjà vu...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What a strange feeling..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Maybe we didn't sleep very well last night, or maybe we slept too much."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm sorry, Dunyarzad, but I need to leave for a moment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "Oh, sure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? Where are you going? You're just gonna walk off like that?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
