    "300805": {
        "Desc": "Go to Lambad's Tavern",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "A feeling of... déjà vu?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon knows what that is! It's when you feel like you've already experienced whatever is going on..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "In that case, Paimon also felt something like that today... But that's just our brains playing tricks on us, isn't it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So, why'd you run here in such a hurry?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I want to do something I normally never would."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I want to see if I can get rid of this déjà vu."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So that's it! You're intentionally doing things you usually wouldn't, and seeing if you still get that same feeling of déjà vu..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lambad",
                    "T": "Welcome, you two! Are you here for lunch? What would you like to eat?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "One Charcoal-Baked Ajilenakh Cake, please."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lambad",
                    "T": "Got it. You don't look like you're from these parts, but I gotta say, you've got good taste. I'll give this order to the kitchen."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Charcoal-Baked Ajilenakh Cake! Isn't it that... that burned thing that didn't look tasty at all?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh... Paimon understands what you're trying to do now... You'd never normally order something like this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "After some time, the Charcoal-Baked Ajilenakh Cake is served..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That... thing... Are you really gonna eat it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Isn't this... going a bit too far..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Here goes!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "H—How was it? The look on your face is telling Paimon that it tasted awful..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "No... It actually tasted really good."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Then, you mean..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "This flavor..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I've definitely eaten this before."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's impossible! We were just talking about how gross it looked..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...So would this be a case of taste bud déjà vu?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I couldn't get rid of it after all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Looks like I tried this before."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon also gets the impression that we've been here many times, even though we aren't regulars."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Umm... How about... we go out again and try something else."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
