    "300806": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Dunyarzad",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, Dunyarzad is sitting by herself on that bench over there..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What a coincidence, Dunyarzad! We meet again! Uh, why are you sitting here all by yourself?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "Oh, I ran into some kidnappers just now, but thankfully, Dehya came to my rescue. I started to feel unwell after that, so I sat down here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Kidnappers? Oh my goodness! Are you hurt?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "I'm okay. Dehya's arm got scratched, but it isn't serious."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Phew... That's a big relief. But Dunyarzad, you seem a little down today... It's the Sabzeruz Festival, and you've been looking forward to it so much."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "Not at all. I've always been like this. Excessive physical exertion or strong emotions tend to aggravate my illness."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "Besides, no matter how amazing today may be, it is but a single day. After however many more days, my time will come to an end."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon doesn't quite follow you, and Paimon feels like something's really got you down right now..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm so sorry for leaving you behind earlier."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "It really is fine. I don't mind."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I just experienced a number of strange events..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Have you noticed anything out of the ordinary?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "Huh? Did something happen?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Dunyarzad... have you ever felt déjà vu? You know... Like when you've already experienced something that's happening right now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "Déjà vu? No, but my days have been the same for years now. Even if I were feeling déjà vu, I suppose I would already be used to it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, Paimon sees... Then, is it only the two of us...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "It's almost time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? Time for what?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "Nilou's Dance of Sabzeruz is about to begin. Let's go."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "300807": {
        "Desc": "Go to the Grand Bazaar and see the Dance of Sabzeruz",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Azar",
                    "T": "...With your lack of intellectual credentials, I do not believe you are qualified to debate with me. What you should be doing is finding workers to tear down this ridiculous eyesore."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azar",
                    "T": "When we return, have the Scribe draft an ordinance before the next Jnagarbha Day that prohibits public art performances. We will announce it to the public later via the Akasha."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Setaria",
                    "T": "Understood. I will inform him when I return."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azar",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azar",
                    "T": "The Sabzeruz Festival... Go celebrate the birth of that god to your heart's content."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Nilou, are you okay?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nilou",
                    "T": "Oh, Dunyarzad, the Grand Sage ordered us to stop the performance..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "It's okay. There's nothing we can do about it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nilou",
                    "T": "But you've been really looking forward to this. I don't want you to have any regrets..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "It truly is unfortunate, but I don't wanna cause trouble for anyone. Didn't the Grand Sage say that he might investigate the organizers?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nilou",
                    "T": "True, but... *sigh* Well, okay, we'll just have to try again next year, hehe..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "The next festival... I probably won't be around by then."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Nilou",
                    "T": "Wait... What did you just say?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dunyarzad",
                    "T": "No, nothing. I'll be heading back to rest. Thank you for your help, everyone."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon can't believe what those heartless geezers did!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's a real shame."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "For some reason, I felt like this outcome was inevitable."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Did Dunyarzad already go back? We should also return and get some sleep."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "The Sabzeruz Festival was forced to come to an unfortunately abrupt end..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "300808": {
        "Desc": "Return to the accommodation and rest",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So in the end, you still couldn't figure out what that déjà vu feeling was all about?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... Maybe it really was because of exhaustion..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm feeling pretty groggy..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I hadn't thought about it, but my head does feel very heavy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Same here! That's why Paimon stopped thinking about it halfway through the day."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Then how about we settle in and get a good night's sleep. For now, we can chalk things up to exhaustion... We can do more thinking tomorrow!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "*beep*"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Khajeh",
                    "T": "...Observing a modest drop in the output of Jnana Energy, but values still remain within normal parameters."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Azar",
                    "T": "Continue to monitor for variances in the data, and find the cause as soon as possible."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
